    dc:description "FIGURES 5–11. Cis micans (Fabricius, 1792). 5–7. Lectotype of C. crenatus C. R. Sahlberg, 1836. 5—dorsal view; 6—lateral view; 7—labels. 8–11. Lectotype of C. hispidus var. albohispidulus Reitter, 1901. 8—dorsal view; 9—lateral view; 10—frontal view; 11—labels. Photos 5–7 by Pekka Malinen (MZH)." ;
